headline: CF Industries Holdings, Inc. Declares Quarterly Dividend and Confirms Dates for Third Quarter 2025 Results and Conference Call
summary: NORTHBROOK, Ill., October 01, 2025--CF Industries Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: CF) today reported that its board of directors has declared a $0.50 per share dividend on its common stock. The dividend will be payable on November 28, 2025, to stockholders of record as November 14, 2025.
